            <title><![CDATA[【🤧[小白菊]#连打喷嚏又鼻痒流涕或是花粉过敏#】医生提醒，春季花粉过敏高发，出现鼻痒症状，有可能是过敏而非感冒。#花粉过敏别硬扛#，建议易感人群：①在过...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【🤧[小白菊]<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%9E%E6%89%93%E5%96%B7%E5%9A%8F%E5%8F%88%E9%BC%BB%E7%97%92%E6%B5%81%E6%B6%95%E6%88%96%E6%98%AF%E8%8A%B1%E7%B2%89%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%9E%E6%89%93%E5%96%B7%E5%9A%8F%E5%8F%88%E9%BC%BB%E7%97%92%E6%B5%81%E6%B6%95%E6%88%96%E6%98%AF%E8%8A%B1%E7%B2%89%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#连打喷嚏又鼻痒流涕或是花粉过敏#</span></a>】医生提醒，春季花粉过敏高发，出现鼻痒症状，有可能是过敏而非感冒。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%8A%B1%E7%B2%89%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E5%88%AB%E7%A1%AC%E6%89%9B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%8A%B1%E7%B2%89%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E5%88%AB%E7%A1%AC%E6%89%9B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#花粉过敏别硬扛#</span></a>，建议易感人群：①在过敏季来临前10-14天，遵医嘱使用抗过敏药物；②花粉指数高时减少户外活动，外出做好必要防护，戴口罩、防护镜；③回家后，清洗鼻腔、脸、手等裸露皮肤；④花粉季少开窗，尽量不在室外晾衣服、床单等👇🏻 （央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5012464706715689" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hnsiqgseupj61dz0s4kcx02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/By8gKnfelx08dk2fztGg01041200PrHo0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710726943&amp;ssig=y7xBNUth2m&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/MchcSQKmlx08dk2fAefm01041200qEW30E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710726943&amp;ssig=Akn8L4DNks&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/GXgjCBEelx08dk2fmSxa01041200giQs0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710726943&amp;ssig=HAXrriANF2&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5012464706715689" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
